      <title>债券收益率因美国数据下滑；亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚和新西兰债券上涨，追随美国国债的涨势，此前疲软的制造业数据增强了人们对美联储今年将降息的预期。亚洲股市有望下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 22:36:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
